Defendant Brandon M. Kline in court with attorney Anthony D Cotton.  Kristi J Gordon appeared for the State of Wisconsin.    Attorney Cotton requests the Court the Defendant remain out on bail pending appeal.  The Court denies the request for reasons stated on the record. The Defendant was sentenced to the following:

IMPOSED SENTENCE of: 

5 YEARS IMPRISONMENT;
  -  3 YEAR(S) OF INITIAL CONFINEMENT; (THE DEFENDANT IS TO REPORT TO THE WAUKESHA SHERIFF'S DEPARTMENT ON DECEMBER 26,2015 BY 5:00 P.M.)
  -  2 YEAR(S) OF EXTENDED SUPERVISION;

CONDITIONS OF EXTENDED SUPERVISION:  
*Any appropriate terms imposed by agent;
*Comply sex offender registry for 15 years; (may be extended by agent if appropriate);

IMAGE SURCHARGE:  Two Images @ $500.00 each for a total of $1000.00;

COURT COSTS:  $268.00 (to be paid as a condition of extended supervision);

DNA SURCHARGE:  $250.00 (to be paid as a condition of extended supervision);

Defendant is not eligible for Challenge Incarceration Program.
Defendant is not eligible for Substance Abuse Program.

Felony warnings, voting rights and firearms warnings given.
